      "title": "[Boing Boing] Ginsberg's 1959 Howl album returns for his 100th birthday",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/AllenGinsburg_HOWL_LPMock.jpg?fit=1200%2C789&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/AllenGinsburg_HOWL_LPMock.jpg?fit=1200%2C789&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<a href=\"https://boingboing.net/2026/06/09/ginsbergs-1959-howl-album-returns-for-his-100th-birthday.html\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Ginsberg&#039;s 1959 Howl album returns for his 100th birthday\"><img alt=\"Allen Ginsberg HOWL (Craft Recordings)\" class=\"webfeedsFeaturedVisual wp-post-image\" height=\"789\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/AllenGinsburg_HOWL_LPMock.jpg?fit=1200%2C789&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto; margin-bottom: 5px;\" width=\"1200\" /></a><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Allen Ginsberg would have turned 100 this month, and his own voice reading \"Howl\" is coming back to vinyl. Craft Recordings is <a href=\"https://craftrecordings.com/products/allen-ginsberg-howl-and-other-poems-green-blend-eco-friendly-lp\">reissuing Howl and Other Poems</a> — the spoken-word album Fantasy Records first released in 1959 — on September 4, reproducing the original package design on \"eco-friendly green blend vinyl.\" &#8212; <a class=\"read-more\" href=\"https://boingboing.net/2026/06/09/ginsbergs-1959-howl-album-returns-for-his-100th-birthday.html\">Read the rest </a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://boingboing.net/2026/06/09/ginsbergs-1959-howl-album-returns-for-his-100th-birthday.html\">Ginsberg&#039;s 1959 Howl album returns for his 100th birthday</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://boingboing.net\">Boing Boing</a>.</p>",
